wmsLayer.title: GA0305 Governor Head 1m
wmsLayer.description: This layer is a bathymetry of the survey area near Governor Head from marine surveys GA0303, GA0305, GA0309 and GA0312, collected around Jervis Bay, New South Wales. The data is gridded at one metre resolution. A total of eleven areas were surveyed at various resolutions. The colour ramp for the WMS is stretched between 2-60 metres water depth. The geocat number for this dataset is http://services.ga.gov.au/metadata-gateway/metadata/record/72004.
